{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"24e0669512","title":"对陈伯达《无产阶级世界观和资产阶级世界观的斗争》一文的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1c98adb3a7","index":1,"year":1959,"month":10,"day":16,"articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"312914a5bf","index":0,"year":1959,"month":10,"day":11,"articleId":"24e0669512"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"76fe0cb58e","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈伯达，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央政治研究室主任、《红旗》杂志总编辑。"},{"id":"6967880b3b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一、二是对陈伯达1959年10月9日送审的这篇文章修改稿的批语；本篇三是对陈伯达10月13日送审的这篇文章修改稿的批语。"},{"id":"f4c8b29814","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"康生，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央文教小组副组长。乔本，即胡乔木，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"ebf1b48b0e","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈伯达这篇文章的原题为《请看彭德怀同志的政治面貌》，毛泽东在陈伯达10月9日的送审稿上将题目改为《资产阶级的世界观，还是无产阶级的世界观》。这篇文章后来又改题为《无产阶级世界观和资产阶级世界观的斗争》，发表在《红旗》1959年第二十二期上。中共中央1959年12月13日还将这篇文章印发给各级党委。"},{"id":"017cea2063","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。林，指林彪，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"47e2c14626","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"32aec3daaa","type":"title","text":"对陈伯达！《无产阶级世界观和资产阶级世界观的斗争》一文的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"76fe0cb58e","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志；","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"6967880b3b","type":"paragraph","text":"此件看了，很好。略有修改。如能找康生、乔木以二同志谈一下，可能进一步改得好一点","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"f4c8b29814","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"ebf1b48b0e","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"017cea2063","type":"paragraph","text":"原题没有抓住本质，改一下为好。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"47e2c14626","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"e6713cbadb","type":"paragraph","text":"办理。伯达同志阅后，送周、朱、林三同志一阅，然后交尚昆同志","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"812d3ff78b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"},{"id":"635367c419","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十六日","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512"}],"page":{"id":"298058effb","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"24e0669512","start":437,"end":438}}}},"__N_SSG":true}